        <li><p>Modify the hash function for strings to use positional weightings.</p></li>

        <li><p>We used a hash function for strings that weighted the characters by
            position. Devise an alternative weighting scheme. What are the biases
            that exist with these functions?</p></li>

        <li><p>Research perfect hash functions. Using a list of names (classmates,
