                the following algorithms:</p>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>bubble sort</li>
                    <li>selection sort</li>
                    <li>insertion sort</li>
                    <li>Shell sort (you decide on the increments)</li>
                    <li>merge sort</li>
                    <li>quicksort (you decide on the pivot value)</li>
            </ul></p>
        </li>

